VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
BN-'aDM ChVD ChYDH VMShL MShL 'aL-BYTh YShUr'aL.
V'aMUrTh KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH HNShUr HGDVL GDVL HKNPhYM 'aUrK H'aBUr ML'a HNVTShH 'aShUr-LV HUrQMH B'a 'aL-HLBNVN VYQCh 'aTh-TShMUrTh H'aUrZ.
'aTh Ur'aSh YNYQVThYV QTPh VYBY'aHV 'aL-'aUrTSh KN'yN B'yYUr UrKLYM ShMV.
VYQCh MZUr'y H'aUrTSh VYThNHV BShDH-ZUr'y QCh 'yL-MYM UrBYM TShPhTShPhH ShMV.
VYTShMCh VYHY LGPhN SUrChTh ShPhLTh QVMH LPhNVTh DLYVThYV 'aLYV VShUrShYV ThChThYV YHYV VThHY LGPhN VTh'ySh BDYM VThShLCh Ph'aUrVTh.
VYHY NShUr-'aChD GDVL GDVL KNPhYM VUrB-NVTShH VHNH HGPhN HZ'aTh KPhNH ShUrShYH 'yLYV VDLYVThYV ShLChH-LV LHShQVTh 'aVThH M'yUrGVTh MT'yH.
'aL-ShDH TVB 'aL-MYM UrBYM HY'a ShThVLH L'yShVTh 'yNPh VLSh'aTh PhUrY LHYVTh LGPhN 'aDUrTh.
'aMUr KH 'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH ThTShLCh HLV'a 'aTh-ShUrShYH YNThQ V'aTh-PhUrYH YQVSS VYBSh KL-TUrPhY TShMChH ThYBSh VL'a-BZUr'y GDVLH VB'yM-UrB LMSh'aVTh 'aVThH MShUrShYH.
VHNH ShThVLH HThTShLCh HLV'a KG'yTh BH UrVCh HQDYM ThYBSh YBSh 'yL-'yUrGTh TShMChH ThYBSh.
VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
'aMUr-N'a LBYTh HMUrY HL'a YD'yThM MH-'aLH 'aMUr HNH-B'a MLK-BBL YUrVShLM VYQCh 'aTh-MLKH V'aTh-ShUrYH VYB'a 'aVThM 'aLYV BBLH.
VYQCh MZUr'y HMLVKH VYKUrTh 'aThV BUrYTh VYB'a 'aThV B'aLH V'aTh-'aYLY H'aUrTSh LQCh.
LHYVTh MMLKH ShPhLH LBLThY HThNSh'a LShMUr 'aTh-BUrYThV L'yMDH.
VYMUrD-BV LShLCh ML'aKYV MTShUrYM LThTh-LV SVSYM V'yM-UrB HYTShLCh HYMLT H'yShH 'aLH VHPhUr BUrYTh VNMLT.
ChY-'aNY N'aM 'aDNY YHVH 'aM-L'a BMQVM HMLK HMMLYK 'aThV 'aShUr BZH 'aTh- 'aLThV V'aShUr HPhUr 'aTh-BUrYThV 'aThV BThVK-BBL YMVTh.
VL'a BChYL GDVL VBQHL UrB Y'yShH 'aVThV PhUr'yH BMLChMH BShPhK SLLH VBBNVTh DYQ LHKUrYTh NPhShVTh UrBVTh.
VBZH 'aLH LHPhUr BUrYTh VHNH NThN YDV VKL-'aLH 'yShH L'a YMLT.
LKN KH-'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH ChY-'aNY 'aM-L'a 'aLThY 'aShUr BZH VBUrYThY 'aShUr HPhYUr VNThThYV BUr'aShV.
VPhUrShThY 'yLYV UrShThY VNThPhSh BMTShVDThY VHBY'aVThYHV BBLH VNShPhTThY 'aThV ShM M'yLV 'aShUr M'yL-BY.
V'aTh KL-MBUrChV BKL-'aGPhYV BChUrB YPhLV VHNSh'aUrYM LKL-UrVCh YPhUrShV VYD'yThM KY 'aNY YHVH DBUrThY.
KH 'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH VLQChThY 'aNY MTShMUrTh H'aUrZ HUrMH VNThThY MUr'aSh YNQVThYV UrK 'aQTPh VShThLThY 'aNY 'yL HUr-GBH VThLVL.
BHUr MUrVM YShUr'aL 'aShThLNV VNSh'a 'yNPh V'yShH PhUrY VHYH L'aUrZ 'aDYUr VShKNV ThChThYV KL TShPhVUr KL-KNPh BTShL DLYVThYV ThShKNH.
VYD'yV KL-'yTShY HShDH KY 'aNY YHVH HShPhLThY 'yTSh GBH HGBHThY 'yTSh ShPhL HVBShThY 'yTSh LCh VHPhUrChThY 'yTSh YBSh 'aNY YHVH DBUrThY V'yShYThY.
